{"tid":1694230,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[一人一信救華記]新加坡自古以來都係屬於中國","createTime":"2019-11-05T04:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T11:53:03.000Z","uid":49016,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"e3df740137e373dc2bc1a318cd9ea0622e2bda79","tid":1694230,"uid":49016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"依家draft緊信，希望幫到華記，以下係論點<br />\n<br />\n現時新加坡大部份居民均為中國人<br />\n<br />\n當中大多為明清民初時代到南洋打工既移民後代<br />\n<br />\n所以新加坡人全部都係中國人<br />\n<br />\n就如昨晚央視主播所講，新加坡人既祖國係中國<br />\n<br />\n與祖國搞對抗只會粉身碎骨<br />\n<br />\n中國近年已經大力提倡言論同集會自由<br />\n<br />\n新加玻以言入罪屬獨裁國家行為，與祖國發展方向背道而馳。<br />\n<br />\n請新加玻立即釋放華記<br />\n<br />\n否則我等愛國愛黨份子將會罷買新加玻貨品，以免助長一切分裂國家份子既行為。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be0cc5623544b69b3eecd02300a0f2c82ee835f","tid":1694230,"uid":199926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yvH7LCC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyvH7LCC.png&h=85bed1e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n約定你11月6 Sogo崇光百貨感謝祭 下午三點銅鑼灣見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691137</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"32f183ab6982efd667297a333659de03d584f4eb","tid":1694230,"uid":189046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T04:57:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新加坡作為中國一部分"},{"pid":"dadd4f79c624233af087dce8ac5c418e839f3c3b","tid":1694230,"uid":49016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T05:00:54.000Z","msg":"最緊要轉上微博"},{"pid":"bce88f2ac9df6ed41a71b02749634ae4805935c7",